title: My Nature
typeOfFood: Vegan, American, Organic, Raw, Salad bar, Juice bar, Take-out
description: A raw food salad bar, juice bar, and grocery market, established since 2013. Features a salad bar, daily lunch specials, fresh juices and smoothies, wild green drinks, and wheatgrass grown in-house. Grocery and market offers supplements and takeout items. This is a seasonal operation, so please check ahead for hours.
